{
  "description": "Frozen source-of-truth inventory of SSE event names and Redis stream event types. Consumed by the backend contract test (backend/tests/unit/test_sse_event_inventory_contract.py) and the frontend contract test (frontend/src/lib/sse-event-inventory.contract.test.ts). DO NOT edit any value here without updating docs/architecture/sse-event-inventory.md, both backend constant modules, and both frontend constant maps in the same PR. Names are string-frozen for the entire migration (frozen until Phase 8).",
